BUWAHAHAHAHA

If you guys (the people who actually take the time to even bother reading this) suddenly find out one day that I've killed myself, don't be surprised.

I hate it here.  This house.  This life.  The only good things that actually keep me here, is (strangely enough) school, and the friends I've met at school that are actually doing more for me than I think they're realizing.

My parents have failed to notice that maybe all the stress they're putting on me is making me shut down further.  True, a certain amount of pressure is a good thing, but I'm sorry, telling me EVERY FUCKING DAY that if I don't shape up, they're pulling me from Carroll is doing FUCK ALL for my psycological well being.  I am so sick and tired of feeling this way.  And then I was listening to the last unicorn today and that just made me wish for a time where I was a straight A student, did everything on time, and had parents that were pleased with me.

When did it all decide to go to hell in a handbasket?

I
